);font-size:12px;background:rgb(242,242,242)\"><br/></span></p><p><br/></p></div>'),(6,'发展历程','{i-2}:<p><span style=\"color: rgb(121, 121, 121); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1.2017年中央一号文件首次将“推进农村电商发展”单独提出 2.当前，我国农业正经受农业资源部分闲置、开发过度、污染加重的考验 3.互联网+开创了大众参与的众筹模式，对于我国农业现代化影响深远。 4.采用线上线下结合的双向O2O模式：走进农村带动工业品下行，走出农村助力农特产品上行。</span></p>'),(7,'合伙人','{i-2}:<div style=\"background:#f2f2f2;\"><p style=\"line-height: 24px; text-align: center; background: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(71,71,71);font-size:12px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\";text-align:center;line-height:24px;background:rgb(242,242,242)\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);font-size: 21px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">哮天犬，是一个有梦想的平台</span></span></strong></p><p style=\";text-align:center;line-height:24px;background:rgb(242,242,242)\"><span style=\";font-size:16px\\\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">哮天犬的宗旨</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\\\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">：通过自己的努力和服务，以一个</span>“互联网<span style=\"font-family:color:#003399;font-size:16px;\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">”的应用工具，让有梦想的您实现</span></span><span style=\";font-size:16px\\\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">创业</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\\\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，让服务</span></span><span style=\";font-size:16px\\\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">变得有意义</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px; text-align: center; background: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><img src=\"/uploadfile/ueditor/image/20170725/1500960412296781.png\" title=\"1500960412296781.png\"/><span style=\";font-family:Helvetica;color:rgb(71,71,71);font-size:12px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\";text-align:center;line-height:24px;background:rgb(242,242,242)\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);font-size: 21px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">梦想合伙人打造计划</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px; text-align: center; background: rgb(242, 242, 242);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(71,71,71);font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">哮天犬的平台属性，决定了可速性的发展。公司计划在</span>2017年底前，完成一个区县建设的标杆作用，用户累积百万，推动及落实宜宾地区县域经济的建设布局，实现平台经济过千万。在2018年完成平台的技术升级，完善升级电商服务及精准扶贫工作，落实可复制制度，参与全川电子商务执行工作，实现大众创新、万人创业的团队建设目标，促进公司发展。</span></p><p style=\";text-align:center;line-height:24px;background:rgb(242,242,242)\"><span style=\";font-family:Helvetica;color:rgb(0,213,255);font-size:12px\">-----------------------------</span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);font-size: 16px\">梦想合伙人 &nbsp;→ &nbsp;镇级服务站（展示店） &nbsp;→ 县级运营中心（公司制）</span></strong><span style=\";color:\\#337FE5\\\">签订合同</span></p><p style=\";text-align:center;line-height:24px;background:rgb(242,242,242)\"><span style=\";font-family:Helvetica;color:rgb(0,213,255);font-size:12px\">------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</span></p><p style=\";text-align:center;line-height:24px;background:rgb(242,242,242)\"><img src=\"/uploadfile/ueditor/image/20170725/1500960424907814.png\" title=\"1500960424907814.png\"/></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);font-size: 16px\">梦想</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);font-size: 16px\">合伙人</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);font-size: 16px\">的条件：</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">1、年龄介于18-</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">40</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">岁之间，男女不限；</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 160px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">2、本地户籍居民；</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">3、在当地人脉关系好，人缘好；</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">4、为人热心，愿意为他人服务；</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 160px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">5、会电脑、</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">能</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">打字、会上网；</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 160px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">6、有创业精神、电商意识；</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;7、有5000元保证金的经济能力；</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 160px; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">8、诚信服务，无不良记录。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 64px; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);font-size: 16px\">梦想合伙人的福利</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);font-size: 16px\">：</span></strong><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">拥有平台管理权限；</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 64px; text-indent: 176px; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">区域品牌践行者；</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 64px; text-indent: 176px; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">县域经济收益合伙人；</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 64px; text-indent: 176px; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">五险一金受益人；</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 64px; text-indent: 176px; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">区域创业明星；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px; text-align: center; background: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><img src=\"/uploadfile/ueditor/image/20170725/1500960434216134.png\" title=\"1500960434216134.png\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">主要职能：</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">1、</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">线上线下服务</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">：由于客观原因，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">经培训合格了的村、社的合伙人要对所负责区域的</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">居民提供专业的</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">农产品上行服务，也要落实需求</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">导购，代购服务，让不懂网购，甚至没有电脑，不会上网的群众也能享受</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">电商</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的便利。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">2、物流中转：农村物流网点覆盖远低于城市。</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">合伙人执行线上线下</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">服务的同时，也</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">要</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">充当了物流中转的角色</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">及调度</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，帮助广大群众</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">解决</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;“收</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">发</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">货难</span>”的</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">相关</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">问题。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">3、市场推广：</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">合伙人</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">作为当地人流和信息流集散地</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的职业经纪人</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">要有责任地把农户的农产品及相关产品推介给平台面向大众，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">更可将</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">集市</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">商城省钱、方便及正品的购物体验以及商城最新的促销活动第一时间传播给周围居民</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，做到卖不愁、买放心的服务落地</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">4、售后服务：</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">为农户提供资金安全到手的保障，也</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">为周围居民提供商城订单退换货，保修等问题，解决</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">相关</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的难题</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；农产品平台承诺有损伤无理由退款不退货的服务。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">5、普及电商：</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">合伙人要运用</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">培训</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">学习的</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">专业</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">电商知识</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">帮助</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">周围居民</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">熟悉</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">网上</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">产品销售技能及</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">购物的</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">基</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">础知识</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；并充分运用市场对称信息提升农户销售品的经济价值，减少网购商品的费用，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">为</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">他们当好</span>“管家”</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">6、信息采集：</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">合伙人</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">将所在地区的大宗购物需求信息</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">收集整理</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，由</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">营运中心</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">提供专业化、个性化的采购方案。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">7、便民服务：</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">合伙人</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">服务站将陆续推出</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">网约用车</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、缴费</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><s