lvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, STHeiTi, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; cursor: pointer; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 18.768px; line-height: 30.0288px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在五化联盟系统中，所有奖金均以电子货币形式体现，分别是电子币、报单币、云币。电子币能转化成报单币和云币，但不能逆转。电子币也可以在系统中提现，但要收取10%的手续费;报单币只能在会员发展新会员注册单时使用，云币只能在系统内购买“五化联盟”的股票。</div><div style=\"font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, STHeiTi, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; cursor: pointer; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 18.768px; line-height: 30.0288px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; height: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, STHeiTi, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; cursor: pointer; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 18.768px; line-height: 30.0288px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; cursor: pointer; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><p class=\"lazy_before\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; cursor: pointer; max-width: 100%; margin: 10px auto; padding: 493.766px 0px 0px; border: 0px; width: 719.094px; height: 0px; position: relative;\"><img class=\"lazy qf-slider\" fake_src=\"http://pic1.ybvv.com/attachment/forum/201707