iased; cursor: pointer; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 18.768px; line-height: 30.0288px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; height: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 18.768px; line-height: 30.0288px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">还有前几个月的魏则西事件等等这些说明浦田医院是专门作恶的这样的医院毫无医德可言他们只要钱不会管病人的健康！</span></p><div style=\"font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, STHeiTi, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; cursor: pointer; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 18.768px; line-height: 30.0288px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; height: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 18.768px; line-height: 30.0288px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1浦田医院敢于拿钱买病人而且很舍得一二医院门口的医托把病人骗到浦田医院然后拿到高额的回扣。</span></p><div style=\"font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, STHeiTi, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; cursor: pointer; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 18.768px; line-height: 30.0288px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; height: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 18.768px; line-height: 30.0288px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2浦田医院也善于搞公关因为他们有钱。这种医院没什么技术但是吹牛皮很厉害专门忽悠人，来不来就说你这个病不及时医治就要转化为癌症！浦田医院有很多共同的特征其实很容易鉴别。</span></p><div style=\"font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, STHeiTi, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; cursor: pointer; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 18.768px; line-height: 30.0288px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; height: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 18.768px; line-height: 30.0288px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3舍得拿钱打广告，比如公交车上，电视上，车站旁的广告上，电台广告，还有就是乡下到处路上墙上的广告，在城里到处发杂志和所谓的优惠卡。这样的医院一般都是浦田医院。</span></p><div style=\"font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, STHeiTi, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; cursor: pointer; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 18.768px; line-height: 30.0288px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; height: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 18.768px; line-height: 30.0288px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4.这样的医院一般都设有网络部，就是和百度推广，现在百度搜索里所谓的商业推广，这种医院的网站做的比较花哨点进网站会有所谓的在线医生主动联系你，实际上那些人哪里是医生啊只是网络医托而已哈。</span></p><div style=\"font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, STHeiTi, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; cursor: pointer; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 18.768px; line-height: 30.0288px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; height: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 18.768px; line-height: 30.0288px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">5.当你进去这种医院的时候他们会想尽所有办法让你尽快交钱，交了钱就跑不脱了撒，哪里的医生也会有意无意的说些话来吓你让你尽快交钱住院.</span></p><div style=\"font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, STHeiTi, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; cursor: pointer; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 18.768px; line-height: 30.0288px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; height: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 18.768px; line-height: 30.0288px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">符合以上5点的应该都是这种医院哈。</span></p><div style=\"font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, STHeiTi, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; cursor: pointer; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 18.768px; line-height: 30.0288px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; height: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 18.768px; line-height: 30.0288px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">希望对大家有所帮助。大家也可以以此为参照来甄别身边的黑心医院对钱对身体都是有好处的。据我所知宜宾这样的黑心医院有很多的哈！</span></p><div style=\"font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, STHeiTi, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; cursor: pointer; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 18.768px; line-height: 30.0288px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; height: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 18.768px; line-height: 30.0288px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">感谢您的赏脸阅读</span></p><div style=\"font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, STHeiTi, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; cursor: pointer; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 18.768px; line-height: 30.0288px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; height: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 18.768px; line-height: 30.0288px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">网友的原贴已经被删除无法看到</span></p><p><br/></p>','宜宾零距离'),(141,1,26,'<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; font-family: SimSun; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); white-space: normal; widows: 1; overflow: visible !important; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://a1.huanqiu.cn/images/7b595e12e2faea9f8b52119344edbe7b.jpg\" style=\"border: none; max-width: 572px; height: auto; overflow: hidden; margin: 30px auto 10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 23px auto 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; font-family: SimSun; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); white-space: normal; widows: 1; overflow: visible !important; text-align: center;\">宜宾县人民政府副县长肖萍宣布比赛正式开始</p><p style=\"margin: 23px auto 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; font-family: SimSun; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); white-space: normal; widows: 1; overflow: visible !important; text-align: center;\">为充分展示宜宾县柏溪镇良好的人文地理环境、风土人情、精神风貌。广泛提升少峨郊野公园的知名度和美誉度,带动市民全民参与、全民健身,激发蓬勃发展正能量。由中共柏溪镇委员会,柏溪镇人民政府主办,四川烈焰信息科技有限公司策划,宜宾博道体育发展有限公司等单位共同打造的“少峨氧吧 徒步郊野”2017少峨郊野公园越野徒步赛于7月22日在宜宾县柏溪镇举行。</p><p style=\"margin: 23px auto 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; font-family: SimSun; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); white-space: normal; widows: 1; overflow: visible !important; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://a1.huanqiu.cn/images/d1efb1e10b8b83b2fd41881ceb2ef25f.jpg\" style=\"border: none; max-width: 572px; height: auto; overflow: hidden; margin: 30px auto 10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 23px auto 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; font-family: SimSun; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); white-space: normal; widows: 1; overflow: visible !important; text-align: center;\">徒步赛正式开始,参赛选手冲出起点</p><p style=\"margin: 23px auto 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; font-family: SimSun; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); white-space: normal; widows: 1; overflow: visible !important; text-align: center;\">此次比赛出席开幕式和闭幕式的领导和嘉宾有宜宾县县委常委、统战部部长宋庆伍,宜宾县人民政府副县长肖萍,柏溪镇党委书记王涛,柏溪镇党委副书记、镇长聂涛,四川烈焰信息科技有限公司总经理袁天势,宜宾市航空运动协会会长余建英,宜宾市登山协会会长钟奏凯,宜宾市自行车运动协会秘书长王萍等。</p><p style=\"margin: 23px auto 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; font-family: SimSun; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); white-space: normal; widows: 1; overflow: visible !important; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://a1.huanqiu.cn/images/76ee42a349036e96e21a70d1602ad553.jpg\" style=\"border: none; max-width: 572px; height: auto; overflow: hidden; margin: 30px auto 10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 23px auto 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; font-family: SimSun; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); white-space: normal; widows: 1; overflow: visible !important; text-align: center;\">本次少峨郊野公园徒步赛有来自成都、重庆、云南、河北、新疆、海南、广西、广东、绵阳、广元、资阳、内江、自贡、乐山、泸州等地500余名选手参加,其中有上至69岁的长者和下至5岁的小朋友,还有带上宝宝和父母全家参与的。参赛选手在8公里的赛程中,从柏溪镇金沙广场出发后,经金沙江边——街心花园——古寨天梯健身步道——古寨门——放生池,最后进入少峨村文化广场,有宽阔公路,有天梯步道,有林间小路,有田埂小道,领略了少峨郊野公园的佛教文化、兵寨文化、田园文化、体育文化,感受到不一样的风土人情和生态环境。</p><p style=\"margin: 23px auto 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; font-family: SimSun; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); white-space: normal; widows: 1; overflow: visible !important; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://a1.huanqiu.cn/images/8e8b1c8c81df5b9ba9efc124e9b7acf5.jpg\" style=\"border: none; max-width: 572px; height: auto; overflow: hidden; margin: 30px auto 10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 23px auto 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; font-family: SimSun; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); white-space: normal; widows: 1; overflow: visible !important; text-align: center;\">参赛选手行走在林间小道</p><p style=\"margin: 23px auto 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; font-family: SimSun; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); white-space: normal; widows: 1; overflow: visible !important; text-align: center;\">每一位走到终点的选手都领到了组委会精心制作的完赛奖牌和纪念礼品。闭幕式上,颁奖嘉宾分别为男子组和女子组的前10名发了纪念品；为鼓励大家积极投入环保公益中,本次徒步赛还评选出了5名环保大使颁发了纪念品。当地的农户自发准备了土鸡、土鸭、兔子、土鸡蛋、新鲜蔬菜和水果等作为特色奖品,以抽奖的形式送给此次比赛的参赛选手。</p><p style=\"margin: 23px auto 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; font-family: SimSun; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); white-space: normal; widows: 1; overflow: visible !important; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://a1.huanqiu.cn/images/8ccc7e436627bbe9fc4ef15db6acbcc8.jpg\" style=\"border: none; max-width: 572px; height: auto; overflow: hidden; margin: 30px auto 10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 23px auto 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; font-family: SimSun; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); white-space: normal; widows: 1; overflow: visible !important; text-align: center;\">为获奖选手颁奖</p><p style=\"margin: 23px auto 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; font-family: SimSun; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); white-space: normal; widows: 1; overflow: visible !important; text-align: center;\">正值三伏天,少峨山顶凉爽,但城区依然闷热,为保障参赛选手的安全,组委会特意为每名参赛选手购买了运动意外险,还为每一名参赛选手准备了矿泉水、仁丹、藿香正气液等防暑药品,在比赛途中设立了4个补给点和医疗点,100多名工作人员和志愿者为参赛选手提供服务保障。</p><p style=\"margin: 23px auto 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; font-family: SimSun; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); white-space: normal; widows: 1; overflow: visible !important; text-align: center;\">在风情的少峨郊野公园里,拥有柑橘、樱桃、葡萄、翠冠梨、茵红李、蔬菜等原生态水果和蔬菜基地。七月,正是翠冠梨、茵红李、葡萄等水果的采摘期。在闭幕式现场,当地农户还准备了水果品尝,并邀请参赛选手前往采摘基地,让参赛选手尽享原生态的美味。此外,当地各具特色的农家乐,也拿出了看家本领,准备了拿手好菜和好酒,让参赛选手享受到农家田园风味,回味无穷。</p><p style=\"margin: 23px auto 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; font-family: SimSun; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); white-space: normal; widows: 1; overflow: visible !important; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://a1.huanqiu.cn/images/4ba21851331065af66477119a93d129b.jpg\" style=\"border: none; max-width: 572px; height: auto; overflow: hidden; margin: 30px auto 10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 23px auto 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; font-family: SimSun; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); white-space: normal; widows: 1; overflow: visible !important; text-align: center;\">据了解,此次大赛的举办地少峨郊野公园,由一山(少峨山)一湖(少娥湖)的自然景观组成,山体巍峨,主峰秀丽,汇聚成一片绿色的海洋,七月的少峨郊野公园,更是植物茂盛,百花争艳,形成了一个天然氧吧。景区还有保存有较为完整的两座寺庙和一座建于宋末时期的古军寨。近年来,宜宾县柏溪镇镇大力发展构建“体育+旅游”的大文化产业,带动农户增收致富。少峨郊野公园是宜宾县政府重点投入和打造的近郊景区,在不断完善景区内各类设施配备,也将继续开展更多的体育文化旅游项目活动。此次徒步赛的举办,旨在有效吸引旅游人群,提升旅游产业价值,将少峨郊野公园打造成宜宾县文化产业的靓丽名片。</p><p><br/></p>','南方网'),(142,1,26,'<table width=\"580\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"width: 844px;\"><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><td align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"yellowuang\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 10px 30px; width: 500px; border: 1px solid rgb(255, 204, 94); background-color: rgb(255, 253, 246);\">推荐阅读</div></td></tr><tr><td align=\"left\" class=\"content14\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://pic3.newssc.org/upload/ori/20170626/1498459469471.jpg\" style=\"border: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; text-align: center;\">游客穿梭于荷塘</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>四川新闻网宜宾6月26日讯（石兴旺 摄影报道）</strong>昨（25）日，以“大妙和花，荷花大妙”为主题的宜宾江安大妙第四届荷花旅游节隆重开幕。数千名游客慕名前往，冒雨体验当地以千亩荷莲为主题的乡村特色旅游。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 16px;\">据了解，当地举办荷花旅游节是为进一步挖掘文化旅游资源，倾力打造“大妙荷花”品牌，以此助推生态农业和乡村旅游业的持续发展。今年的荷花旅游节时间自6月25日到7月2日，其中6月28日至30日为摇滚音乐啤酒节，7月2日为国家四类钓鱼比赛。</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table width=\"580\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"width: 844px;\"><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><td align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"yellowuang\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 10px 30px; width: 500px; border: 1px solid rgb(255, 204, 94); background-color: rgb(255, 253, 246);\">推荐阅读</div></td></tr><tr><td align=\"left\" class=\"content14\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://pic3.newssc.org/upload/ori/20170626/1498459500281.jpg\" style=\"border: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; text-align: center;\">雨中荷花别样美</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 16px;\">游客在大妙除了可以赏荷钓鱼外，大妙的泥巴腊肉和花地湾原生态梨膏也值得一尝，此外花地湾水库、女娲洞、白岩沟、古戏楼、白云庵、五子登科等自然风景也让人流连忘返。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 16px;\">“大妙荷花比较出名嘛，听说旅游节开幕了，我们就专门过来感受一下。”一位专程从外地赶来参加此次旅游节的王女士评价说，大妙的荷花节办得越来越好了，文化活动也相当精彩。</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table width=\"580\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"width: 844px;\"><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><td align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"yellowuang\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 10px 30px; width: 500px; border: 1px solid rgb(255, 204, 94); background-color: rgb(255, 253, 246);\">推荐阅读</div></td></tr><tr><td align=\"left\" class=\"content14\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://pic3.newssc.org/upload/ori/20170626/1498459556004.jpg\" style=\"border: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; text-align: center;\">一名摄影师静心拍摄荷花</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 16px;\">据悉，近年来大妙乡依托于大石母河系得天独厚的自然资源，当地已种植观赏莲藕500余亩、食用莲藕1500亩。通过整合部门资金300万元，自筹资金200万元，大妙乡相继完善了荷花广场、区间道路和旅游公厕等基础和公共服务设施，大力推进乡村旅游发展和农民致富增收。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 16px;\">据大妙乡政府不完全统计，连续几届荷花旅游节带来的旅游收入年均约1500万元，仅此一项即实现全乡人均纯收入年均增长100余元。下一步，大妙乡还将努力创建国家AA级景区，将大妙打造成宜宾知名的乡村旅游盛地。</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table width=\"580\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"width: 844px;\"><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><td align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"yellowuang\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 10px 30px; width: 500px; border: 1px solid rgb(255, 204, 94); background-color: rgb(255, 253, 246);\">推荐阅读</div></td></tr><tr><td align=\"left\" class=\"content14\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://pic3.newssc.org/upload/ori/20170626/1498459582025.jpg\" style=\"border: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; text-align: center;\">大妙荷花旅游节开幕式现场</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table width=\"580\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><td align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"yellowuang\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 10px 30px; width: 500px; border: 1px solid rgb(255, 204, 94); background-color: rgb(255, 253, 246);\">推荐阅读</div></td></tr><tr><td align=\"left\" class=\"content14\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://pic3.newssc.org/upload/ori/20170626/1498459615799.jpg\" style=\"border: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; text-align: center;\">精彩的文艺表演</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><br/></p>','四川新闻网'),(144,1,24,'<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: left; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 30px; margin: 0px 3px 15px;\">我省出台《关于进一步加强就业创业工作的意见》</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: left; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 30px; margin: 0px 3px 15px;\">华西都市报讯（四川日报记者刘春华本报记者李媛莉）日前省政府出台《关于进一步加强就业创业工作的意见》（以下简称意见），要求从扩大就业规模、稳定就业岗位、促进创业带动就业等方面，加强全省就业创业工作。这是记者6月13日从省政府召开的全省就业创业工作暨2013年高校毕业生就业工作电视电话会议上获悉的。</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: left; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 30px; margin: 0px 3px 15px;\">省级财政设小微企业信用贷款风险补偿金</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: left; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 30px; margin: 0px 3px 15px;\">为给小微企业成长壮大营造良好的发展环境，增加就业岗位，全省将进一步完善财政支持小微企业发展的融资政策，对符合小额担保贷款政策条件的劳动密集型小微企业贷款，可由小额担保贷款担保基金提供担保，贷款额度最高可达200万元，财政部门按照人民银行公布的基准利率的50%给予贴息。</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: left; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 30px; margin: 0px 3px 15px;\">我省将建立小微企业信用贷款风险补偿制度，省级财政设立小微企业信用贷款风险补偿金，鼓励银行类金融机构扩大对小微企业的融资支持。小微企业在领取营业执照1年内，可缓缴社会保险费。</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: left; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 30px; margin: 0px 3px 15px;\">企业有困难可申请缓缴社保费</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: left; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 30px; margin: 0px 3px 15px;\">意见提出，城乡劳动者居家灵活就业人员，可参加城镇职工基本养老和基本医疗保险。</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: left; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 30px; margin: 0px 3px 15px;\">为稳定就业岗位，意见提出，统筹地区在确保社会保险待遇按时足额发放的前提下，对符合产业政策、合法经营、参加社会保险的企业，当生产经营出现暂时性困难，暂时无力缴纳社会保险费时，报经批准，可缓缴养老、医疗、失业、工伤、生育五项社会保险费，缓缴期限最长不超过6个月。</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: left; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 30px; margin: 0px 3px 15px;\">企业开展岗前培训可获补贴</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: left; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 30px; margin: 0px 3px 15px;\">为鼓励企业开展岗前培训和技能提升培训，我省将督促企业依法建立和完善现代企业职工培训制度，对新录用人员结合就业岗位要求开展岗前培训，并按有关规定给予培训补贴。</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: left; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 30px; margin: 0px 3px 15px;\">围绕产业发展和技术升级大规模开展在岗职工技能提升培训的企业，将得到一定补贴。对参加培训并获得技师、高级技师职业资格证书的在岗职工，按规定给予培训补贴。以高校毕业生、返乡农民工、退役军人、就业困难人员、残疾人为重点，开展“提升创业能力专项行动”。</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: left; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 30px; margin: 0px 3px 15px;\">我省将面向城乡各类有培训愿望的劳动者，开展多种形式的就业技能培训，组织未继续升学的应届初高中毕业生开展劳动预备培训，提升技能水平和就业能力。在高等院校推广“学业证书”和“职业资格证书”并行制度，提升高校毕业生的职业技能水平和就业创业能力。</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: -webkit-center; white-space: normal; widows: 1;\"><br/></p><p><br/></p>','华西都市报'),(145,1,25,'<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 37px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 方正小标宋简体; font-size: 29px;\">--</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">何文毅一行赴北京参加</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 21px;\">“<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">一带一路</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">”</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">中小企业国际合作论坛暨项目与资本对接洽谈会</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.ybnysty.gov.cn/UploadFiles/2017-07/2/2017072117134922873.png\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\">“一带一路”中小企业国家合作高峰论坛现场</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">为</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">推进园区发展，贯彻落实国家一带一路发展战略，</span>&nbsp;7<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">月</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Calibri;\">20</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">日，受中国中小企业协会“一带一路”工作委员会邀请，宜宾国家农业科技园区党工委副书记、管委会主任何文毅一行赴北京参加《</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 21px;\">&nbsp;“<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">一带一路</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">”</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">中小企业国际合作论坛暨项目与资本对接洽谈会</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">》，并与</span>“一带一路”中小企业协会进一步洽谈合作事宜。园区管委会副主任陈胜军参加了论坛及洽谈活动。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; line-height: 39px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">本次高峰论坛由中国中小企业协会和中国银行业协会主办，中国中小企业协会</span>“<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">一带一路</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">”</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">工作委员会承办。论坛秉承</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">“</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">一带一路</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">”</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">倡议共商、共建和共享的精神，旨在助力区域经济和广大中小企业深度融入</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">“</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">一带一路</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">”</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">建设，加强国际园区间的合作，促进产融结合，积极参与全球资源配置。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">“</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">一带一路</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">”</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">沿线国家的代表、国内地方政府代表、近三十家金融机构代表、近百家来自全国各地的企业界代表以及数十位专家学者近千人参加本次高峰论坛。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; line-height: 39px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本次论坛，何文毅一行首先听取了</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">全国社保基金理事会副理事长王忠民先生致开幕词并就中小企业在</span>“<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">一带一路</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">”</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">建设中开展国际合作的主题发表</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">的</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">主旨演讲</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">、</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">中国中小企业协会副会长刘纪恒阐述</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">的</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">中国中小企业协会践行</span>“<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">一带一路</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">”</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">倡议</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">、</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">国家发展和改革委员会西部开发司巡视员欧晓理对</span>“<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">一带一路</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">”</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">倡议的精神做</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">的</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">精辟地分析</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">等丰富的主题演讲，参与了专家现场</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 21px;\">“<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">智库对话企业</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">”</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">环节</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">以及各园区、政府项目推介活动、新产业联盟成立启动活动等。</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; line-height: 39px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">随后，在</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">王忠民副理事长、乌兰察布市王国相市长、丝路研究规划中心副理事长蒋志刚、中国人民银行金融研训院院长刘钊和中国金融杂志社首席记者孙芙蓉等嘉宾的见证下</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">，</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">园区管委会主任何文毅</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">与</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 21px;\">“<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">一带一路</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">”</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">工作委员会主任商世伟</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">签订了双方战略合作意向书。本次签约，以</span>“优势互补、资源共享、互惠互利、合作共赢”作为合作的理念和宗旨，借助</spa